title: Trouble In Paradise For Banji Judge And Boyfriend, Yuvraj Thakur?
text:
facebook 637 SHARES 
Bani Judge was locked up in the Bigg Boss house for 105 days and, while boyfriend Yuvraj Thakur had shared an adorable picture of the two while she was inside , it looks like all is not well between the two. 
If Yuvraj's post on Instagram is anything to go by, we are sensing trouble. A photo posted by Yuvraj Thakur (@yuv_thehuman) on Jan 31, 2017 at 12:43am PST 
We hope this isn't a subtle hint at his and Bani's relationship troubles. Photo credits: BCCL
